China-U.S. Chamber of Commerce investigated the New Village Construction in Guanyun County, Lianyungang City\n\n

  	&nbsp;

  	On&nbsp;8th&nbsp;May,&nbsp;the&nbsp;president&nbsp;of&nbsp;China-U.S.&nbsp;Chamber&nbsp;of&nbsp;Commerce,&nbsp;Wynn&nbsp;Wang,&nbsp;led&nbsp;the&nbsp;delegation&nbsp;to&nbsp;Guanyun&nbsp;County.&nbsp;A&nbsp;grand&nbsp;signing&nbsp;ceremony&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;New&nbsp;Village&nbsp;Construction&nbsp;Project&nbsp;was&nbsp;held&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;county&rsquo;s&nbsp;administration&nbsp;center.&nbsp;The&nbsp;municipal&nbsp;standing&nbsp;committee&nbsp;and&nbsp;secretary,&nbsp;Tiefei&nbsp;Tang,&nbsp;gave&nbsp;a&nbsp;speech.&nbsp;The&nbsp;head&nbsp;of&nbsp;Guanyun&nbsp;County,&nbsp;Zheqiang&nbsp;Yin,&nbsp;hosted&nbsp;and&nbsp;county&nbsp;leaders,&nbsp;Yi&nbsp;Sun,&nbsp;Qinjia&nbsp;Wang,&nbsp;Zhenghuai&nbsp;Zhu&nbsp;also&nbsp;attended.  

data:image/png;base64,

  	&nbsp;

  	According&nbsp;to&nbsp;Mr.&nbsp;Tang,&nbsp;Guanyun&nbsp;County&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;fast&nbsp;developing&nbsp;city&nbsp;with&nbsp;supporting&nbsp;industries,&nbsp;competitive&nbsp;market&nbsp;and&nbsp;willing&nbsp;to&nbsp;cooperate.&nbsp;The&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;economy&nbsp;here&nbsp;is&nbsp;increasingly&nbsp;expanding,&nbsp;and&nbsp;a&nbsp;port&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;zone&nbsp;mainly&nbsp;involved&nbsp;chemical&nbsp;industries,&nbsp;heavy&nbsp;industries&nbsp;and&nbsp;new&nbsp;energy&nbsp;has&nbsp;already&nbsp;taken&nbsp;60&nbsp;square&nbsp;kilometers&nbsp;out&nbsp;of&nbsp;​​140&nbsp;square&nbsp;kilometers&nbsp;as&nbsp;planned.&nbsp;The&nbsp;area&nbsp;of&nbsp;an&nbsp;economic&nbsp;development&nbsp;zone&nbsp;with&nbsp;advanced&nbsp;manufacturing&nbsp;as&nbsp;main&nbsp;body&nbsp;has&nbsp;reached&nbsp;25&nbsp;square&nbsp;kilometers.&nbsp;Industries&nbsp;like&nbsp;ship&nbsp;manufacturing,&nbsp;machinery&nbsp;manufacturing,&nbsp;fine&nbsp;chemicals,&nbsp;metal&nbsp;products,&nbsp;and&nbsp;textiles&nbsp;and&nbsp;clothing&nbsp;have&nbsp;become&nbsp;the&nbsp;local&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;leaders,&nbsp;taking&nbsp;advantage&nbsp;of&nbsp;abundant&nbsp;technical&nbsp;workers,&nbsp;sufficient&nbsp;labor&nbsp;force&nbsp;and&nbsp;low&nbsp;cost.&nbsp;Modern&nbsp;service&nbsp;industries&nbsp;are&nbsp;developing&nbsp;fast&nbsp;and&nbsp;widely&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;north&nbsp;of&nbsp;Jiangsu&nbsp;Province&nbsp;which&nbsp;is&nbsp;able&nbsp;to&nbsp;provide&nbsp;professional&nbsp;marketing&nbsp;support&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;regional&nbsp;logistics&nbsp;center.&nbsp;In&nbsp;recent&nbsp;years,&nbsp;10&nbsp;acres&nbsp;of&nbsp;land&nbsp;have&nbsp;been&nbsp;greened,&nbsp;2.1&nbsp;acres&nbsp;of&nbsp;land&nbsp;is&nbsp;covered&nbsp;by&nbsp;followers.&nbsp;An&nbsp;efficient&nbsp;agricultural&nbsp;base&nbsp;will&nbsp;soon&nbsp;be&nbsp;formed&nbsp;in&nbsp;Jiangsu&nbsp;Province.  

  	Tang&nbsp;said,&nbsp;China-U.S.&nbsp;Chamber&nbsp;of&nbsp;Commerce&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;representative&nbsp;organization&nbsp;of&nbsp;American&nbsp;business&nbsp;elites.&nbsp;It&nbsp;contributes&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;cooperation&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;enterprises&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;two&nbsp;countries.&nbsp;This&nbsp;investigation&nbsp;visit&nbsp;is&nbsp;an&nbsp;extremely&nbsp;great&nbsp;beginning&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;two&nbsp;signed&nbsp;investment&nbsp;projects&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;the&nbsp;cornerstone&nbsp;of&nbsp;future&nbsp;development.&nbsp;Guanyun&nbsp;County&nbsp;is&nbsp;ready&nbsp;to&nbsp;embrace&nbsp;the&nbsp;chances&nbsp;and&nbsp;challenges&nbsp;coming&nbsp;with&nbsp;the&nbsp;trend&nbsp;of&nbsp;globalization.  

  	
  	Mr.Yin&nbsp;stated&nbsp;that&nbsp;Guanyun&nbsp;expected&nbsp;for&nbsp;further&nbsp;communications&nbsp;and&nbsp;more&nbsp;extensive&nbsp;cooperation&nbsp;with&nbsp;entrepreneurs&nbsp;from&nbsp;overseas&nbsp;and&nbsp;home,&nbsp;meanwhile,&nbsp;he&nbsp;also&nbsp;truthfully&nbsp;hoped&nbsp;that&nbsp;China-U.S.&nbsp;Chamber&nbsp;of&nbsp;Commerce&nbsp;can&nbsp;introduce&nbsp;Guanyun&nbsp;to&nbsp;more&nbsp;individuals&nbsp;and&nbsp;groups.  

  	
  	President&nbsp;Wang&nbsp;said&nbsp;that&nbsp;Guanyun&nbsp;enjoys&nbsp;a&nbsp;board&nbsp;prospective&nbsp;of&nbsp;development&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;great&nbsp;investment&nbsp;environment,&nbsp;and&nbsp;expressed&nbsp;his&nbsp;faith&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;bright&nbsp;future&nbsp;of&nbsp;Guanyun.  

  	&nbsp;

  	The&nbsp;president&nbsp;of&nbsp;Armco&nbsp;iron&nbsp;Company,&nbsp;Roberts,&nbsp;said,&nbsp;the&nbsp;new&nbsp;project&nbsp;invested&nbsp;in&nbsp;Guanyun&nbsp;will&nbsp;definitely&nbsp;take&nbsp;advantage&nbsp;of&nbsp;Guanyun&rsquo;s&nbsp;location&nbsp;and&nbsp;transportation,&nbsp;bring&nbsp;in&nbsp;the&nbsp;American&nbsp;experts,&nbsp;management&nbsp;and&nbsp;technology,&nbsp;and&nbsp;set&nbsp;a&nbsp;successful&nbsp;example&nbsp;of&nbsp;China&nbsp;New&nbsp;Village&nbsp;Construction.&nbsp;He&nbsp;expected&nbsp;mutual&nbsp;trust&nbsp;and&nbsp;looked&nbsp;for&nbsp;closer&nbsp;cooperative&nbsp;relationship.
